{"type":"message_start","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d84a","toolName":"mcp","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nmember_id: C4\ncase_id: arb-ex11a-20260630135427\nphase: deliberation\nopportunity_id: deliberation:1:C4\nremaining_ms: 886295\nattempts_remaining: 3\njson: {\"case_id\":\"arb-ex11a-20260630135427\",\"member_id\":\"C4\",\"ok\":true,\"result\":{\"evidence\":[{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T14:05:52Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_241b442bed15_submitted-evidence-05-defendant-241b442bed15\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-05-defendant-241b442bed15.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Provides the exact mirrored NOTAM wording and Q code/category for A1010/26 and replacement A1015/26. Relevant to whether the instrument was an aerodrome/airport-operations closure rather than a broad airspace closure, and to conflicts with secondary reports about which airports remained operational.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T14:06:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"241b442bed1566db9088fa4e9dd159b18a0afcafef11dc3cc63d5db9b4564b02\",\"size_bytes\":2852,\"source_description\":\"Captured text from public Notamify OIIX NOTAM pages opened during defendant arbitration investigation; Notamify is an unofficial NOTAM mirror, not the original Iranian AIS publication.\",\"source_url\":\"https://notamify.com/notams/OIIX/693f2d0f-54d3-433b-8128-49f5475ba269 and https://notamify.com/notams/OIIX/67435351-52f9-4d17-8f4c-497a21dd94bf\",\"storage_name\":\"24/241b442bed1566db9088fa4e9dd159b18a0afcafef11dc3cc63d5db9b4564b02\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"defendant\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"Notamify raw OIIX A1010/26 and A1015/26 NOTAM mirror\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T14:03:08Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_51569ad0cb54_submitted-evidence-04-plaintiff-51569ad0cb54\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-04-plaintiff-51569ad0cb54.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Official aviation authority context for non-weather security risk, affected Iranian airspace, and temporary airspace closures/restrictions by states during the conflict; corroborates that the relevant aviation disruptions were conflict/security related, not weather.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T13:56:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"51569ad0cb54f847f57c566a8aa45572ff0e4c29f8a8c22912b8a1b992b49ced\",\"size_bytes\":1592,\"source_description\":\"Captured text from official EASA conflict zone information bulletin page opened during arbitration investigation.\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.easa.europa.eu/en/domains/air-operations/czibs/2026-03-r13\",\"storage_name\":\"51/51569ad0cb54f847f57c566a8aa45572ff0e4c29f8a8c22912b8a1b992b49ced\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"EASA CZIB 2026-03-R13 Middle East airspace bulletin\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T14:02:57Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_57917ec86ba3_submitted-evidence-02-plaintiff-57917ec86ba3\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-02-plaintiff-57917ec86ba3.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Independent contemporaneous reporting that Iran's Civil Aviation Organization announced temporary restrictions over western airspace, severe passenger-flight restrictions, eight airports permitted, daylight-only operations, and individual CAA permits.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T13:57:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"57917ec86ba34e8b03251ce267bf344986ced150fb89d4b8042f412502bd6fe0\",\"size_bytes\":1192,\"source_description\":\"Captured page text from Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty live blog item opened during arbitration investigation; item timestamped 10:03 23.5.2026.\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.rferl.org/a/iran-war-us-hormuz-oil-blockade-gulf-israel/33640284/lbl0lbi456071.html\",\"storage_name\":\"57/57917ec86ba34e8b03251ce267bf344986ced150fb89d4b8042f412502bd6fe0\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"RFE/RL live report: Airspace Closed Over Western Iran, May 23 2026\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T14:02:52Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_ac2309bdc9f7_submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-ac2309bdc9f7\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-ac2309bdc9f7.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Reports the alleged Iranian Civil Aviation Authority NOTAM OIIX A1010/26, effective May 22-May 25, closing western Tehran FIR and limiting operations to eight airports with daylight-only and per-flight approval restrictions.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T13:57:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"ac2309bdc9f7dfe59cccf3ccb80599097c8c2a4dd2b76e47435cf2be49fd05c1\",\"size_bytes\":1872,\"source_description\":\"Captured page text from Indian Express article opened during arbitration investigation; article dated May 23, 2026.\",\"source_url\":\"https://indianexpress.com/article/world/us-news/iran-closes-airspace-trump-cancels-plans-us-military-strikes-rubio-india-10704692/\",\"storage_name\":\"ac/ac2309bdc9f7dfe59cccf3ccb80599097c8c2a4dd2b76e47435cf2be49fd05c1\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"Indian Express report on Iran western airspace NOTAM, May 23 2026\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T14:03:03Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_b762826a22f0_submitted-evidence-03-plaintiff-b762826a22f0\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-03-plaintiff-b762826a22f0.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Aviation-risk context showing OIIX/Tehran FIR status, partial reopening/western closure in June 2026, and tha