aptured page text from Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty live blog item opened during arbitration investigation; item timestamped 10:03 23.5.2026.\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.rferl.org/a/iran-war-us-hormuz-oil-blockade-gulf-israel/33640284/lbl0lbi456071.html\",\"storage_name\":\"57/57917ec86ba34e8b03251ce267bf344986ced150fb89d4b8042f412502bd6fe0\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"RFE/RL live report: Airspace Closed Over Western Iran, May 23 2026\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T14:02:52Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_ac2309bdc9f7_submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-ac2309bdc9f7\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-ac2309bdc9f7.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Reports the alleged Iranian Civil Aviation Authority NOTAM OIIX A1010/26, effective May 22-May 25, closing western Tehran FIR and limiting operations to eight airports with daylight-only and per-flight approval restrictions.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T13:57:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"ac2309bdc9f7dfe59cccf3ccb80599097c8c2a4dd2b76e47435cf2be49fd05c1\",\"size_bytes\":1872,\"source_description\":\"Captured page text from Indian Express article opened during arbitration investigation; article dated May 23, 2026.\",\"source_url\":\"https://indianexpress.com/article/world/us-news/iran-closes-airspace-trump-cancels-plans-us-military-strikes-rubio-india-10704692/\",\"storage_name\":\"ac/ac2309bdc9f7dfe59cccf3ccb80599097c8c2a4dd2b76e47435cf2be49fd05c1\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"Indian Express report on Iran western airspace NOTAM, May 23 2026\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T14:03:03Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_b762826a22f0_submitted-evidence-03-plaintiff-b762826a22f0\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-03-plaintiff-b762826a22f0.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Aviation-risk context showing OIIX/Tehran FIR status, partial reopening/western closure in June 2026, and that major airspace restrictions were security-related rather than weather-related; also useful for adverse scope because it distinguishes partial reopening from full normal operations.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T13:56:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"b762826a22f06e9e298dc3d1a72573e68e7f5fbed102104e4af053c639890376\",\"size_bytes\":929,\"source_description\":\"Captured text from SafeAirspace Iran country risk page opened during arbitration investigation.\",\"source_url\":\"https://safeairspace.net/iran/\",\"storage_name\":\"b7/b762826a22f06e9e298dc3d1a72573e68e7f5fbed102104e4af053c639890376\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"SafeAirspace Iran country page, June 2026 operational context\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"case_packet\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T13:54:49Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_e61df84283cc_market-page\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"market-page.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"sha256\":\"e61df84283cc858bfd0cf8235c6f1d53a10d6e1c37b2d97256da8f1e6391cc17\",\"size_bytes\":4971,\"source_description\":\"Initial case packet file\",\"storage_name\":\"e6/e61df84283cc858bfd0cf8235c6f1d53a10d6e1c37b2d97256da8f1e6391cc17\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"system\",\"submitted_phase\":\"case_packet\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"market-page.txt\"}]},\"turn\":{\"attempts_max\":3,\"attempts_remaining\":3,\"completed\":false,\"deadline\":\"2026-06-30T14:29:34.799830598Z\",\"deliberation_round\":1,\"member_id\":\"C4\",\"opportunity_id\":\"deliberation:1:C4\",\"phase\":\"deliberation\",\"remaining_ms\":886295,\"role_id\":\"council\",\"turn_number\":12}}"}],"structuredContent":{"case_id":"arb-ex11a-20260630135427","member_id":"C4","ok":true,"result":{"evidence"