-weather closure of its airspace by the deadline.","contentIndex":0,"partial":{"api":"openai-completions","content":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"arguments":{"args":"{\"vote\":\"demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"The admitted record proves by preponderance that Iran initiated a major non-weather closure. NOTAM A1010/26 (May 22-25) suspended all civil flight permits in western Tehran FIR, closed all airports in that major region except limited daylight operations with fresh CAA approval, suspended previous permissions, and was security-related. This satisfies the rule's 'broad closure...suspension of commercial flights transiting, arriving in, and departing from... a major Iranian airspace region' with permitted limited exceptions.\"}","tool":"aar_submit_council_vote"},"id":"call_2183","name":"mcp","type":"toolCall"}],"model":"deepseek/deepseek-v3.1-terminus","provider":"openrouter","responseId":"gen-1782828955-TWKa46bPggimynBJq7lO","role":"assistant","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782828955181,"usage":{"cacheRead":51328,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"input":0,"output":0,"total":0},"input":1728,"output":511,"totalTokens":53567}},"type":"text_end"},"message":{"api":"openai-completions","content":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"arguments":{"args":"{\"vote\":\"demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"The admitted record proves by preponderance that Iran initiated a major non-weather closure. NOTAM A1010/26 (May 22-25) suspended all civil flight permits in western Tehran FIR, closed all airports in that major region except limited daylight operations with fresh CAA approval, suspended previous permissions, and was security-related. This satisfies the rule's 'broad closure...suspension of commercial flights transiting, arriving in, and departing from... a major Iranian airspace region' with permitted limited exceptions.\"}","tool":"aar_submit_council_vote"},"id":"call_2183","name":"mcp","type":"toolCall"}],"model":"deepseek/deepseek-v3.1-terminus","provider":"ope