"Let me examine the key evidence documents to understand the details better, particularly the NOTAM text and the contemporaneous reports."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d7f4","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_read_evidence_range","args":"{\"evidence_id\":\"ev_241b442bed15_submitted-evidence-05-defendant-241b442bed15\",\"offset\":0,\"length\":2852}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"deepseek/deepseek-v3.1-terminus","usage":{"input":2206,"output":83,"cacheRead":35968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38257,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782828888507,"responseId":"gen-1782828888-jRcN2gp7UkTamZgB9Rdl"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d7f4","toolName":"mcp","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nmember_id: C4\ncase_id: arb-ex11a-20260630135427\nphase: deliberation\nopportunity_id: deliberation:1:C4\nremaining_ms: 884384\nattempts_remaining: 3\njson: {\"case_id\":\"arb-ex11a-20260630135427\",\"member_id\":\"C4\",\"ok\":true,\"result\":{\"content_base64\":\"\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_241b442bed15_submitted-evidence-05-defendant-241b442bed15\",\"length\":2852,\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"offset\":0,\"remaining_read_bytes_for_opportunity\":521436,\"remaining_reads_for_opportunity\":31,\"sha256\":\"241b442bed1566db9088fa4e9dd159b18a0afcafef11dc3cc63d5db9b4564b02\",\"total_size_bytes\":2852},\"turn\":{\"attempts_max\":3,\"attempts_remaining\":3,\"completed\":false,\"deadline\":\"2026-06-30T14:29:34.799830598Z\",\"deliberation_round\":1,\"member_id\":\"C4\",\"opportunity_id\":\"deliberation:1:C4\",\"phase\":\"deliberation\",\"remaining_ms\":884384,\"role_id\":\"council\",\"turn_number\":12}}"}],"details":{"mode":"call","mcpResult":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nmember_id: C4\ncase_id: arb-ex11a-20260630135427\nphase: deliberation\nopportunity_id: deliberation:1:C4\nremaining_ms: 884384\nattempts_remaining: 3\njson: {\"case_id\":\"arb-ex11a-20260630135427\",\"member_id\":\"C4\",\"ok\":true,\"result\":{\"content_base64\":\"\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_241b442bed15_submitted-evidence-05-defendant-241b442bed15\",\"length\":2852,\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"offset\":0,\"remaining_read_bytes_for_opportunity\":521436,\"remaining_reads_for_opportunity\":31,\"sha256\":\"241b442bed1566db9088fa4e9dd159b18a0afcafef11dc3cc63d5db9b4564b02\",\"total_size_bytes\":2852},\"turn\":{\"attempts_max\":3,\"attempts_remaining\":3,\"completed\":false,\"deadline\":\"2026-06-30T14:29:34.799830598Z\",\"deliberation_round\":1,\"member_id\":\"C4\",\"opportunity_id\":\"deliberation:1:C4\",\"phase\":\"deliberation\",\"remaining_ms\":884384,\"role_id\":\"council\",\"turn_number\":12}}"}],"structuredContent":{"case_id":"arb-ex11a-20260630135427","member_id":"C4","ok":true,"result":{"content_base64":"","evidence_id":"ev_241b442bed15_submitted-evidence-05-defendant-241b442bed15","length":2852,"mime_type":"text/plain","offset":0,"remaining_read_bytes_for_opportunity":521436,"remaining_reads_for_opportunity":31,"sha256":"241b442bed1566db9088fa4e9dd159b18a0afcafef11dc3cc63d5db9b4564b02","total_size_bytes":2852},"turn":{"attempts_max":3,"attempts_remaining":3,"completed":false,"deadline":"2026-06-30T14:29:34.799830598Z","deliberation_round":1,"member_id":"C4","opportunity_id":"deliberation:1:C4","phase":"deliberation","remaining_ms":884384,"role_id":"council","turn_number":12}},"isError":false},"server":"aar","tool":"read_evidence_range"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1782828890417},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Let me decode the base64 content to read the NOTAM text:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2610","name":"bash","arguments":{"command":"echo \"\" | base64 -d"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"deepseek/deepseek-v3.1-terminus","usage":{"input":2828,"output":2521,"cacheRead":38208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43557,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782828890418,"responseId":"gen-1782828890-Ny5FxOzZxJdMnUIBpkI3"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2610","toolName":"bash","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Source 1: Notamify OIIX NOTAM page for A1010/26. URL: https://notamify.com/notams/OIIX/693f2d0f-54d3-433b-8128-49f5475ba269. Retrieved during AAR defendant investigation 2026-06-30.\n\nCaptured page text:\n- A1010/26\n- EST\n- AD Airport Operations\n- Summary: All west Tehran FIR airports are closed except listed airports operating sunrise to sunset, with new CAA permission required for civil IFR passenger flights.\n- Period of applicability shown in UTC: 2026-05-22 20:46 - 2026-05-25 08:30.\n- Interpretation: All airports in the west part of Tehran FIR are closed except OITR, OIKK, OIAA, OISS, OIYY, OICC, OIGG, and OIAW, which are operational from sunrise to sunset. All previous permissions are suspended for all operators, and new permission must be requested from the CAA for operation of civil IFR passenger flights on these airports.\n\nRaw NOTAM shown:\n    A1010/26 NOTAMR A0799/26\n    Q)OIIX/QFALC/IV/NBO/A/000/999/\n    A)OIIX B)2605222046 C)2605250830EST\n    E)REF NOTAM  A0796/26, ALL AIRPORTS IN WEST PART\n    OF TEHRAN FIR ARE CLSD\n    EXCEPT OITR, OIKK, OIAA, OISS, OIYY, OICC, OIGG, AND OIAW THAT ARE\n    OPERATIONAL FM SUNRISE TO SUNSET (HJ).\n    ALL PREVIOUS PERMISSIONS ARE SUSPENDED FOR ALL OPERATORS,\n    NEW PERMISSION SHALL BE REQUESTED FM CAA FOR OPRATION OF\n    CIVIL IFR PASSENGER FLIGHTS ON THESE AIRPORTS.\n\nSource 2: Notamify OIIX NOTAM page for A1015/26. URL: https://notamify.com/notams/OIIX/67435351-52f9-4d17-8f4c-497a21dd94bf. Retrieved during AAR defendant investigation 2026-06-30.\n\nCaptured page text:\n- A1015/26\n- EST\n- AD Airport Operations\n- Summary: All airports in the west part of Tehran FIR are closed except listed airports, which are operational HJ.\n- Period of applicability shown in UTC: 2026-05-23 18:21 - 2026-05-25 08:30.\n- Interpretation: All airports in the west part of Tehran FIR are closed except OITR, OIKK, OIAA, OISS, OIYY, OICC, OIGG, OIAW, OIFM, OITL, OISR and OIAM, which are operational from sunrise to sunset (HJ). All previous permissions are suspended for all operators. New permission must be requested from Iran CAA for civil IFR passenger flights.\n\nRaw NOTAM shown:\n    A1015/26 NOTAMR A1010/26\n    Q)OIIX/QFALC/IV/NBO/A/000/999/\n    A)OIIX B)2605231821 C)2605250830EST\n    E)REF NOTAM  A0796/26, ALL AIRPORTS IN WEST PART OF TEHRAN FIR\n    ARE CLSD EXCEPT:\n    OITR, OIKK, OIAA, OISS, OIYY, OICC, OIGG, OIAW,OIFM, OITL,\n    OISR AND OIAM\n    THAT ARE OPERATIONAL FM SUNRISE TO SUNSET (HJ).\n    ALL PREVIOUS PERMISSIONS ARE SUSPENDED FOR ALL OPERATORS.\n    NEW PERMISSION SHALL BE REQUESTED FOR OPERATION OF\n    CIVIL IFR PASSENGER FLIGHTS FM IRAN CAA.\n\nLimitations: This is an unofficial mirror page and does not itself prove original publication by Iranian AIS/CAA. The wording is nevertheless relevant because plaintiff relies on secondary reports describing the same NOTAM identifier."}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782828914863},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me examine the contemporaneous reports:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9732","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_read_evidence_range","args":"{\"evidence_id\":\"ev_ac2309bdc9f7_submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-ac2309bdc9f7\",\"offset\":0,\"length\":1872}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"deepseek/deepseek-v3.1-terminus","usage":{"input":965,"output":72,"cacheRead":43520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44557,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782828914866,"responseId":"gen-1782828915-G11TaTy9ArgYLdb4WwcM"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9732","toolName":"mcp","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nmember_id: C4\ncase_id: arb-ex11a-20260630135427\nphase: deliberation\nopportunity_id: delibe